title_bed_bats_review: Guesthouse in Sylhet District · 4 bedrooms · 4 beds · 3 baths
listing_description:
Bring the whole family to this great place with lots of room for fun.

Sunapur Mini Resort Sylhet in Sylhet has a garden and a shared lounge. Boasting a shared kitchen, this property also provides guests with a children's playground. At the resort, rooms come with a desk, a terrace with a lake view, a private bathroom, a flat-screen TV, bed linen and towels. The shared bathroom is fitted with a bath. 

The area is popular for cycling, and car hire is available at the accommodation.

title_bed_bats_review: Home in Sylhet · 1 bedroom · 1 bed · 1 shared bath
listing_description: We welcome guests to stay in our home and experience authentic Bangladeshi family life and our homemade, locally sourced food. The beautiful Sreemangal countryside and tea gardens are a short drive away and you can enjoy walking in the local bazars where there is always something interesting to see. We maintain very high standards of hygiene and make sure there is always safe mineral water to drink. At the end of a busy day you can relax in your private room which has its own seating area.
